Animal Shelter Simulator game

1   must be able to track animals in shelter
2   must be able to track resources such as food and bedding
3   must be able to track adoption requests / applications
4   must allow player to match animals to adopters
5   must have graphical interface
6   must have keyboard or button-based controls
7   game should display current score
8   must implement scoreboard that is persistent between plays
9   game will support single-player operations
10  must have end-state, such as when player manually quits or fails 
